&lt;img src="http://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/1608265-1111c41d24b23c1a.png?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/1240"
loading="lazy"
alt="CheatSheet.png"
>&lt;/p>
